{"title":"Manifestaciones cutáneas del VIH-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Manifestaciones cutáneas del VIH-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Manifestaciones cutáneas\\Ndel VIH","guid":"bsK-U3z2xZoGln8DI8vbpQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Historia Natural de la Infección por VIH\\NFases clínicas","guid":"Krth6U5ZSq8XhYCSLspjLw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Primoinfección.","guid":"FoXH9znlumIch0myFsAI4g","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Generalmente asintomática en la mayoría de los casos.","guid":"Ocb9sHCpr-1uyNP0UqF-_A","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Síndrome de\\Nprimoinfección (30%):","guid":"Q89MNGQ0Ahp0HSwxBV21cQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Período de incubación: 2-6 semanas.","guid":"QYMDG3_hQ05UImY7WAjLEg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Síntomas:","guid":"YYl4nXYzkXkAl-MMIwx7uA","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Fiebre.","guid":"T2U5YHXv2lQ78OXoDDGDgw","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Síndrome mononucleósico.","guid":"DM0ZU2QIf5J4lYrQMO3arQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Meningitis viral.","guid":"Q4enI2I0mbFq8g7lc-MYiA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"• Exantema.","guid":"ONeOFW6mmioY3m2rbs0bqw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"6","text":"• Úlceras orales.","guid":"NajimzLj6TduyKorSi_e3g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"2","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"TaNjAT15Volc6oYZeF7E6g","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Serología: Puede ser positiva, negativa o indeterminada.","guid":"dhTUx1S6SUd7FUbKL9vSdw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Carga viral: Alta durante la primoinfección.","guid":"RWP5NGneGr4CfVFzFMkylA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"• CD4: Niveles pueden ser normales o bajos.","guid":"X831Ej5uN1sg-rYXbJsOZg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"2. Latencia clínica.","guid":"GNqBTF67iXMHJwZgaU9m7A","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Inicio:","guid":"QqKrpCF6GVsKncnWawt_pw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Comienza después del síndrome de primoinfección.","guid":"Ina27RmQQOcdiOkTZf5eEA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Ausencia de manifestaciones clínicas visibles.","guid":"e8TamQh69_hZ4XaYNJxorg","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"• Duración:","guid":"HIrB4U83RjV9ecgdHGWFdQ","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Variable: 5-8 años.","guid":"dyGSInK_5EMjaYRZLMp0vg","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Progresores rápidos: 5% (Desarrollo de SIDA en 3-4 años).","guid":"JaPNexIyLoR2-lOcBy1GGA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"• Progresores lentos: 5% (Desarrollo de SIDA en >10 años).","guid":"CGW__XeSNqgqOcHRfnqUxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"16","text":"• Características:","guid":"BLOnGEz9K-oniVnRBolgow","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Replicación viral persistente y masiva.","guid":"TEx_8CVPCJsuVmc7EbB5JA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• Destrucción continua de linfocitos T CD4 con alta capacidad de reemplazo.","guid":"Dy0jWjDTuK4meau5bvsYbA","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"16","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"OGKbsm2Yz7lD2yjEO_IB0w","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Serología: Positiva.","guid":"b0HwCUd0YdBblibSEbim9g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Carga viral: Estable, pero variable.","guid":"YQSiuHkfD-V3twUGXMl9UQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"• CD4: Niveles variables, tendencia a la baja.","guid":"AZoH3VGYe54RZeX_eLuaAA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"1","text":"3. Manifestaciones clínicas.","guid":"PMxKIxbdPv8oF5mqbGQHTQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Inmunodepresión Celular:","guid":"ck9gmWvJ0zNBGyVfKrH8Sw","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Consecuencia directa de la disminución de LTCD4.","guid":"RFhf4jTPalklhg6-afwtXQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Otras Infecciones (dependientes\\Nde la epidemiología local):","guid":"RwGY3RyAYlpxKXN1T2dY2w","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Alta endemia: Infecciones virulentas aparecen más temprano.","guid":"FBKZAhtjNUZN4e2fYF8Y8g","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Mejor saneamiento: Infecciones oportunistas aparecen más tarde.","guid":"QLI94nw4VNtyD5IXT99hPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"• Neoplasias (pérdida de\\Nvigilancia antitumoral):","guid":"LQwNiRiJPdA-2nmoHE39kw","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• VEB: Linfoma no Hodgkin.","guid":"X_2foBpwoHsuBqSJQQJCWA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• HPV: Cáncer cervicouterino y anal.","guid":"E4-wYCW9qZAdy7-pFSm4Pg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• HHV-8: Sarcoma de Kaposi (particularmente en hombres homosexuales).","guid":"d1YlLi8xpakN5VI-O66FEA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"31","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"WWKi7AT2TiNmo_4fHTHvIQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Serología: Positiva.","guid":"ZAEQAjNrYPwlqrJtKwKo3w","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Carga viral: Alta (>100.000 copias/ml), variable.","guid":"T-vDVhbUJeN6agG6Y_5cWA","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"• CD4: Bajo (<200 células/ml), variable.","guid":"MjdbKUhL71pEXXVLcumZCw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Etapificación del VIH/SIDA\\NClasificación en etapas","guid":"FolSuSYJRZMgGkzgaXl9OQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Basada en la clasificación\\Ndel CDC (EEUU).","guid":"HBQUazvk89tv9icrL6PEyw","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Combina criterios clínicos con\\Nsituación inmunológica.","guid":"TvZFMgGjc_AN3k9RLvPk0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Etapas:","guid":"GDqA2X96KqsvLHgqJA0iEQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• A: Asintomático, primoinfección\\No linfadenopatía generalizada.","guid":"YaKdaw3B5tREzX0JWPjCmQ","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Duración: 3-8 semanas.","guid":"I497f1TyWQgNesNuM_XiDA","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• Manifestaciones: Dermatitis seborreica, herpes zóster.","guid":"brx5IBaKdkdgULe4T9zQ0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"• B: Síntomas menores que sugieren inmunodeficiencia\\N(ej. candidiasis orofaríngea, herpes zoster).","guid":"PPOMfVKyz0cUp0eqIPScfw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Duración: >15 años.","guid":"Crfoi2NTfulK83vbHMAQ3Q","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Manifestaciones: Prurito, xerosis, candidiasis oral, moluscos contagiosos.","guid":"E8XOcW6FicpvVg0MeBMB7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"• C: Síntomas mayores o enfermedades definitorias de SIDA\\N(ej. linfoma, neumonía por Pneumocystis jirovecii).","guid":"Bh4wQzpR-hdL90VfVgnzmQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Manifestaciones: Sarcoma de Kaposi, foliculitis eosinofílica, micosis sistémicas,\\Ninfecciones micobacterianas.","guid":"KrqnnzLu4bpbc_IISLNE8g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"45","text":"• Situación inmunológica\\N(CD4/ml):","guid":"USYf-kZhRxk6CE_yA117JA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• A1, B1, C1: CD4 > 500.","guid":"Dq02c35lxT12RxQvUzF6qA","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Síndromes cutáneos agudos.","guid":"DoUPkyKzHc4Ga1udcCes_g","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Leucoplasia oral vellosa.","guid":"MHUEo0s42KdJIG-YbWiRIA","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"• Dermatitis seborreica.","guid":"Heun7l3Ht0IOXS2gJAnYMg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"• Psoriasis.","guid":"GBmxWVpUcv96E8vLaT_RVA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"• Sarcoma de Kaposi.","guid":"ILW6GDQcG71snUx4L2LwjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"57","text":"• A2, B2, C2: CD4 200-500.","guid":"NNLMnzkQDndEwcxnA8kR0Q","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Candidiasis orofaríngea.","guid":"MoHg-mLkYKcClGs0Z1StmQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Herpes zóster.","guid":"G_RvHkdWN5trHb9qVqfxhQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"• Psoriasis refractaria.","guid":"GfZTVB3atg4tb4hXKHti5w","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"• Nevos eruptivos atípicos.","guid":"QI3T3DPa4_UYow_mcQLYfw","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"57","text":"• A3, B3, C3: CD4 < 200 (indicativo de SIDA).","guid":"OrOCZ1KgG7gyvPajVseW0g","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• CD4 < 250/mm³:","guid":"P4s2wGzIl0BBCTy8V6ToGQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Foliculitis eosinofílica.","guid":"fxO8nGHDf35ea2mgHP9kig","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• Dermatitis seborreica severa.","guid":"Rx0KPzsdCIhA5LltZ9LEVw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"• Molluscum contagiosum extenso.","guid":"bzkkRS2CBeUXNbTjIbsFQA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"• Sarcoma de Kaposi, angiomatosis bacilar.","guid":"EGZmjRnKIBgJD7LZLFrVqw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"• Tuberculosis miliar o extrapulmonar.","guid":"YSBXs3QtckQDAscxexarBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"69","text":"• CD4 < 50/mm³:","guid":"EggoUjByT4gjkg3vUpX8Lg","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Ulceraciones herpéticas persistentes.","guid":"ZE0zfTw1HdVDmNSuY2DwGQ","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• Herpes simple mucocutáneo extenso.","guid":"HfidUyIEPk4AYFSkXYPUEw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"• Citomegalovirus diseminado.","guid":"DszVjkFpkWA1KLwsVenfzQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"• Ictiosis adquirida.","guid":"fIaZ6HYNdZo9vKQka7--Lg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones","guid":"cJGRuHo4x-V5RTp6dLRXlQ","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• 100% de los Pacientes: Alguna manifestación en la piel a lo largo de la evolución.","guid":"U4qoclK5zBhzVt7vCWjGFg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Sospechar infección por VIH\\Nen enfermedad cutánea si","guid":"eAwAxzeXWFFD-orSalthYA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Edad atípica","guid":"VnKGGjyFYiQqBAHSbq0G8w","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Localización o morfología atípica","guid":"O_-M0FkwefwSuikEL-m-Jw","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Patologías que no calzan con patrón morfológico → pensar en RAM o sífilis secundaria.","guid":"dJ_jvl9SmTFDTb0rdQomaA","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"Curso prolongado o severo","guid":"L4YaPyOU7G4d_jDEb7HTNA","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• VIH puede presentar con mayor frecuencia o gravedad en manifestaciones cutáneas.","guid":"SgYA6k2Es9EUoBPaB29Yzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"83","text":"No “esperar” factores de riesgo","guid":"EHi9cUjfkEs7Lb42ZANl4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"81","text":"• Tratamientos Habituales: Resistencia y mala respuesta en algunas manifestaciones cutáneas.","guid":"UQhja3E_9yAbTVrxArYfzA","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"81","text":"• Clasificación:","guid":"G5lcYy6EnSVtbCv5E6VdKg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Neoplásicas: Carcinomas y sarcomas.","guid":"dZ25LQ2dP01By1qRWHX8sw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Infecciosas: Infecciones virales, bacterianas y fúngicas.","guid":"ezSbnBWsP3gUF7M8J34oMQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"• No infecciosas: Psoriasis, dermatitis atópica, manifestaciones atípicas.","guid":"aan5cmiXy09LA66XT56AkQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Síndrome de\\NPrimoinfección en VIH","guid":"SskOmUKFAghaUTwgOYvM7A","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Estado Prodrómico:","guid":"OW_872WjPQlmujIQCt1Huw","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Similar a gripal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• CEG, adenopatías","