children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Queratosis seborreica","guid":"CKBCa0u9QMkRNXW_atlD6A","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Carcinoma escamocelular","guid":"LsdD41FTqSpDSmm0Xzi8eQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"• Carcinoma basocelular","guid":"bmeAXzyu7N8AO8bHBbQfeg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"• Papulosis bowenoide","guid":"L1iqhBXzKKoSnnfBL5-ndg","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"117","text":"• Queratoacantoma","guid":"bXXlH3f-zLwrG0AEWqThCw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"117","text":"• Carcinoma cloacogénico","guid":"cXbU9E4VAMMxfdZqU4aoew","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"115","text":"• Características: Más agresivos, rápido progreso, lesiones atípicas","guid":"GbodOjxtNiwb-LxIIlpfpQ","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"115","text":"• Melanoma: Relación no clara con VIH","guid":"CCp29S0uMgcNM6OONvG62A","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"107","text":"3. Sarcoma\\Nde Kaposi","guid":"F619YVqK-7FxSfieJNp3gw","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Tumor endotelial, multifocal, HHV-8 ","guid":"JUWgRmZ66odAPxxINahU5Q","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"4 formas clínicas:","guid":"Kt5ZT3z_UMFFGFXIdd4Mpw","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Clásico (hombres judíos, mediterráneo, este Europa)","guid":"DF-rnh_Wz2BKF4BWbX-wfA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"  Endémico (hombres África)","guid":"QvekPWppbjE-xX3_TDIcjg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Asociado a inmunosupresión (transplante renal)","guid":"D6tMfVJfurZ4cQ2VPpt5Sw","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"  Epidémico (VIH)","guid":"doY16geU_zt6iXUAG30-IA","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Neoplasia más común en VIH,\\Nhombres homo o bisexuales","guid":"LHrnJmdtGvEzh00_UcCHbA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"126","text":"• Prevalencia: 34% en SIDA declarado, menor en portadores","guid":"foHbMVB-DUIWKndRbOlbkA","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"126","text":"• Características:","guid":"fTq_iBdAjCF0dCztbrGUfA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• Tumores violáceos, eritematosos","guid":"DSz6IhZmPhhynXsKPIWkpg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"• Proliferación de células endoteliales","guid":"LFlmwwU78sxsJUwdGc9L4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"126","text":"• Lesiones: nódulos, placas eritemato-violáceas, máculas, pápulas","guid":"ZVWM5SXyA1dCODz3IWf8_g","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"126","text":"• Distribución: cabeza, cuello, tronco, EESS","guid":"fedPsUjXHGU8t9OOF6Fs6w","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"126","text":"• Compromiso: ganglios, tracto GI, pulmones, hígado, bazo, riñón","guid":"BURSkViwj9Y5-8yRDW7Jhw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones Virales","guid":"cPE5yWPnc6lhYBwqHUqgjA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"1. Herpes Simple","guid":"Dr94ACA2rP8zvrPjZTH-Gw","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Manifestaciones: Úlceras crónicas, vesículas, úlceras extensas","guid":"aSNmdU2FaEc3GexuZl4l_Q","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"• Complicaciones: Proctitis herpética en homosexuales","guid":"ZMX0aCuOGVxVD7p6ShuBTQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"• Cofactor: Desarrollo de SIDA","guid":"UYAcsxdH93Frg35MT2dsZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"2. Varicela Zoster","guid":"NvMvsWaZLhNIpVobZnlJ8Q","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"Varicela clásica o complicada","guid":"Ci4agWajit9WKx0lGqbX8w","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Herpes zoster:","guid":"P914gGwWadBewdS4Jflt9w","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"RR 5-7 veces más en VIH, predice inmunodepresión grave","guid":"L4MbKhFY21t-qj3WSxx3jQ","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":">1 dermatomo, necrótico, verrucoso, diseminado, crónico","guid":"HX0gm1zCk0Ivdo7yU_mHmA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"141","text":"3. Citomegalovirus","guid":"","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Manifestaciones: Ulceraciones perianales, infecciones diseminadas (pápulas, máculas purpúricas)","guid":"AOvhsCEEpeFy0i_vBsqjjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"141","text":"4. Epstein-Barr","guid":"dfi8bzPIh-0fM40US-bnzg","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Manifestaciones: Leucoplasia vellosa","guid":"aDQWADcytE4LK0Cbf-GTYQ","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Placas grisáceas, borde lateral de lengua","guid":"XJU7viqmeqt4NXlxc8wgXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Ocurre con CD4 < 300.","guid":"AqGQIATt888CgwUMVCGs0w","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Generalmente asintomática.","guid":"HDXrQG4Gg1gjiRk4fFT_Fw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"153","text":"• Indicador de infección por VIH.","guid":"bhLMo2t4Y8Zk1Ym1XHOyNg","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"141","text":"5. Molusco Contagioso","guid":"JgNWgjehKqJLZdZ3XPaGMw","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Frecuencia: Común en pacientes con VIH.","guid":"DsmsFlXaEVFoBJuzSDmpBg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Manifestaciones: Lesiones atípicas, múltiples, áreas anogenitales o faciales","guid":"Eb2v_3x1OTkkvArlAq7pyQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"• Localización: Cara y zonas intertriginosas.","guid":"Ov0v91Lw_sdB6Y4KOjqFvQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"• Lesiones: Típicas o >1 cm, confluentes.","guid":"e721JCZhYtpjAUVbLc3LkQ","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"• Tratamiento: Mejoran con TARV","guid":"FctULEAJV15MdMD3Wxrd3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"141","text":"6. Papilomavirus","guid":"eq67cRma7UpDD0sqKjHWmw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Frecuente en VIH","guid":"KvPIpUG5iQB1Tk4oatFBJg","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"> genotipos 16 y 18","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"Lesiones múltiples, confluentes","guid":"Lc_y0FQQIuAQyq8dS00TbA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestaciones: Verrugas planas, extensas, anogenitales","guid":"YFys4gYcJw8f-YpVSYATVw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones\\NBacterianas","guid":"FkHVMgqR8ohhuGV_Fy224g","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"1. Staphylococcus aureus","guid":"OpbdS0n2-Mh_AwVvWNE2AA","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Patógeno más común en pacientes VIH.","guid":"Auu17121_1U-GunRbkKpeQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"• Infecciones: Impétigo, foliculitis, forunculosis, celulitis, abscesos, úlceras","guid":"K5aYaVSKlW4d-FpvE8quaQ","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"• Responde bien al tratamiento, pero con alta tasa de recaídas y portación nasal persistente.","guid":"Dm-DrWf7k3wJUYURHTkvxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"170","text":"2. Treponema pallidum\\N(Sífilis)","guid":"JZjUQzhoTK8gKeOFBfWBJg","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• Progresión más rápida en pacientes con VIH.","guid":"C3rIUlPDhhw1TKQ8Bzh9dg","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"• Desarrollo de las 3 etapas en 1 año.","guid":"eiTo9hhN6Zc1BkkID_A9Iw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"• Manifestaciones clínicas más graves.","guid":"WFdA9gF7Cf9rCxsARmoNmQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Características: Chancros múltiples, dolorosos, progresión rápida, resistencia a tratamientos","guid":"C71JvCkjmwoTrEHKHXr5vA","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"• Tratamiento menos eficaz: Requiere dosis más altas de penicilina.","guid":"bPNtxU_gpLUi3b_Qb98jtA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"175","text":"• Falsos positivos y negativos en serología son más comunes.","guid":"LZakCmD4qaFeIc0tPAYnuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"170","text":"3. Bartonella hensalae","guid":"TEEsbwKde8Z_H4OefRPikg","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"• Angiomatosis bacilar: Presentación típica.","guid":"dzv50RH2zSUT8IAJArbCIw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"• Manifestaciones: Tumores vasculares, nódulos gomosos en piel y mucosa oral","guid":"PoRzvkAjbdpPdZR9EiYDFA","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"• Diseminación: Puede afectar piel, hígado, bazo y otros órganos.","guid":"YYsN3D71iKFvz3lbOeJO0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"170","text":"4. Micobacteriosis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• Infecciones: TBC miliar, nódulos subcutáneos, linfadenitis ulceradas","guid":"Fzbknn9TzdJKjYbTGdh0vg","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"170","text":"5. Neisseria gonorrhoeae:","guid":"WMlzAj6yMEYAHNUTGN5hig","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Mayor riesgo de infección diseminada en pacientes con VIH.","guid":"SPQ9HmdzUj5ZP1d8Bsnh6w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones Fúngicas\\Ny Levaduras","guid":"BEHBoU0Qi99t-iGSIHes4g","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"1. Candidiasis","guid":"Ui6mjzzq1UIEvl4STjfPSQ","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Frecuencia: Muy común en pacientes con VIH.","guid":"Krs5ECMqHDwdQyQaWFHdGw","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Manifestaciones: Placas blanquecinas adherentes, pseudomembranosas\\Nen mucosa oral, erosiones profundas, compromiso GI y vaginal","guid":"OxcPNxGDOsoczKv5UVjkaQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Orofaringea (la más común), esofágica, respiratoria.","guid":"YthDhm2XXE9T4OTnO6G2iQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Vulvovaginitis en mujeres.","guid":"LEmMlVP9ufpUgBgTI4WGZg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• Balanopostitis y candidiasis perianal.","guid":"ZfSHH2hwmBwmPEiJS67aYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"191","text":"• Síntomas: Puede presentarse con o sin síntomas.","guid":"Ma28YTAriCIrjhaYEzjKPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"190","text":"2. Dermatofitosis","guid":"TUZ5K29HU_NTSJs2K0iihQ","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Manifestaciones: Tiñas cutáneas extensas, infección ungueal","guid":"HBUtUn6FEXhohptLR6vFuw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"Más frecuentes que en la población general","guid":"Mboph1SCRG0D-YdQDcfsZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"190","text":"3. Criptococosis","guid":"CTnAVlG_qgJIYltGTBh6LA","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Cryptococcus neoformans","guid":"IwR4tQmuToMQjD59YuUAoA","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"  Levadura ambiental oportunista","guid":"cCXIpGYZo3ME7_BwQlRvNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"Infección pulmonar  con diseminación meníngea (más común) o cutánea (10%):","guid":"DP3O5gDQjQFdXGXVWkRIEg","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"201","text":"• Manifestaciones: Lesiones del color de la piel, úlceras, nódulos, pápulas","guid":"Uw-m5gZ-9bpbdnQkXszwog","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"201","text":"Pápulas o nódulos muy similares a moluscos contagiosos","guid":"Sv-zWA9gWtxavnmXVDlzrw","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"201","text":"Diagnostico con biopsia","guid":"Urvvr1GzkGImoisyTL2RhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"208","parent":"190","text":"4. Histoplasmosis, Esporotricosis, Coccidioidomicosis,\\NAspergilosis, Actinomicosis","guid":"J4sCnhxxzeNbMOYtZg92XA","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• Infecciones sistémicas","guid":"L6KQxG8ite58R-peVTtlBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"190","text":"5. Malassezia\\Nfurfur:","guid":"QY5pPGlvYOdJXCpYV4zQqA","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"• Dermatitis seborreica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Más frecuente en pacientes con VIH que en la población general.","guid":"KGjUA3sQqIZEmXxfEm5IdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"• Presentación: Puede ser típica o atípica (inflamatoria, extensa).","guid":"f9rDlDV8YONPg2PNCyPUXA","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"210","text":"• Características: Placas eritematosas, grasas, en surco nasogeniano, alas nasales, cuero cabelludo","guid":"D9OMI3uetq1Os7cBSuqbWg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"210","text":"• Características: Enrojecimiento, caspa en cejas, alrededor de la nariz, pestañas, comisuras.\\NEn VIH: afecta cara, cuello y tronco.","guid":"Ry11uyYI7hBFF_i8Q97DQg","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"210","text":"• Tratamiento: Corticosteroides tópicos, antifúngicos.","guid":"ZGLYf0XvzcltCvfvCind3w","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"puede ser resistente.","guid":"AdW5i2tlb8hGD3XoPVHIIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"210","text":"• Asociación: Suele vincularse\\Ncon foliculitis del tronco.","guid":"A49mIVY2fHsgWNlWOCsqXQ","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":" Foliculitis pustular eosinofílica ","guid":"TtbKhVsZ1Q0WEKwFOy7L_w","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"Inflamación de folículos pilosos, prurito intenso. Posible reacción a Malassezia furfur o fármacos.","guid":"KNrCCk0P0I9Vz0crewDygQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones parasitarias","guid":"CTp4USVB3ksTmjy3LD7xBg","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"Sarcoptes scabiei\\NSarna típica o noruega","guid":"LvAsziQmezQPI_GmO-37tQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"0","text":"Otras manifestaciones\\Ncutáneas","guid":"e8pPGnPyz9txbB-_clCFBA","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"1. Dermatitis Seborreica:","guid":"WfMD11s34PsYOyrrVXrS7g","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":" Ictiosis Adquirida:","guid":"YHVGJjlXWCxgSN40RNgepQ","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"Piel seca, prurito, resistente a antihistamínicos","guid":"DSHxd2uAYvocQ3_DKTceyQ","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"Piel seca con escamas (“piel de pescado”). ","guid":"f0cl9U1T1iNPAfyEeZYWCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"Asociada a VIH, infecciones, hipotiroidismo, neoplasias.","guid":"Nyk3kVdqU_xYvO2XfJFe9Q","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"225","text":"• Tratamiento: Hidratación intensiva, tratamiento de la causa subyacente.","guid":"NUuKK0za5TscCpH0H5jWnw","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"225","text":"Evaluar en pacientes mayores de 50 años y solicitar exámenes para descartar hepatitis, linfoma, leucemia, anemia y VIH.","guid":"U-T_BgO2mdlRs86ONFpFLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"223","text":"Psoriasis","guid":"cMW6SUyBMhpupGtufSVl5w","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"Más severa con CD4<200","guid":"bFgBeji768VqpRZkL0-ltw","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"• Características: Placas extensas, queratodermia palmoplantar","guid":"agV0cgTKGw5w4uSEPRUbWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"223","text":"Sd de Reiter ","guid":"JccFYDRfIkx67LwZc68K2A","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• Características: Artritis reactiva que puede acompañarse de uretritis, conjuntivitis, lesiones en piel.","guid":"UiYwd17RVK4QOQL_fEaHRA","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"• Tratamiento: AINEs, antibióticos si se sospecha infección.","guid":"RNGIqnoExDsiMS0rHsSMgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"223","text":"Erupción papular pruriginosa del SIDA ","guid":"KCWL1AJVmGtsdWmfGOtGHg","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"223","text":"RAM: melanoniquia por zidovudina","guid":"E9XA0gC1wmlqfnG2NvsayQ","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"223","text":"Lesiones\\NVasculares","guid":"DkBsHzzocQlezSjDG2Jdlg","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"1. Vasculitis Sistémicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"• Manifestaciones: Periarteritis nodosa, angeítis granulomatosa, necrotizante","guid":"C0kQyExZWKgb4gv6OuuhjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"239","text":"2. Pseudotromboflebitis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"• Características: Púrpuras, telangectasias, dolorosas","guid":"O3wOlhgp9lkQJwaTYwcRNA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"223","text":"Alteraciones en\\NPelo y Uñas","guid":"BA8BRhKhtXJuNLoIE-KNaQ","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"1. Pelo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"• Manifestaciones: Alopecia, efluvios telógenos, encanecimiento prematuro","guid":"NJvEPGtX7MFJFoeRETD_-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"2. Uñas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Manifestaciones: Onicomicosis, estriaciones transversales, bandas pigmentadas","guid":"Ff5nbEFMAQIE_SBXP_iv6Q","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":248,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Manifestaciones cutáneas del VIH-2024-1","id":"map_1156","resolved_references":[]}